<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/18(Thu) Equal-gender racing team plots F1 entry in 2026/ Airline Passenger Behavior (Host: Jenny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=730&amp;p=758#p758"><![CDATA[
Equal-gender racing team plots F1 entry in 2026/ Airline Passenger Behavior (Host: Jenny)<br /><br /><br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br />**** NEW*** Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30 Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00 discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05 Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30 discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00 Individual Presentation (each person will have two minutes to give a presentation on any topic of that day.<br />)<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session1: Equal-gender racing team plots F1 entry in 2026<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/equal-gender-racing-team-plots-f1-entry-in-2026/10449560/amp/">https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/equa ... 49560/amp/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1.Do you think that gender equal  has been achieved entirely in Taiwan? <br /><br />2.Are there stereotypes of gender issue still exist in some certain employments?                                                  <br /><br />3.Have you or someone you know ever been treated unfairly because of the gender? Please share with us if any.                          <br /><br />4.Free sharing with your observations in any aspects of gender equal.<br /><br /><br />Session 2:Airline Passenger Behavior Is Getting Even More Out Of Control<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.thestreet.com/investing/airline-passenger-behavior-is-getting-even-more-out-of-control">https://www.thestreet.com/investing/air ... of-control</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br /><br />1.While traveling with airplane, what insensible passenger behaviors have you ever encountered?<br /><br />2.What kind of behavior is the most intolerable with you?                  <br /><br />3.Are you willing to assist the flight attendants to eliminate the bad behaviors if necessary?                  <br /><br />4.The post-COVID life has been unfolded, free sharing with your overseas traveling plans.  <br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Mon May 15, 2023 3:31 pm</p><hr />
